      "url": "/documentation/appkit/nstrackingareaoptions",
      "abstract": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The data type defined for the constants specified in the "
        },
        {
          "type": "codeVoice",
          "code": "options"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " parameter of "
        },
        {
          "type": "reference",
          "isActive": true,
          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstrackingarea/1524488-initwithrect"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". These constants are described below; you can specify multiple constants by performing a bitwise-OR operation with them. In particular, you must supply one or more of the tracking-type constants (that is, "
        },
        {
          "type": "reference",
          "isActive": true,
          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstrackingareaoptions/nstrackingmouseenteredandexited"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", "
        },
        {
          "type": "reference",
          "isActive": true,
          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstrackingareaoptions/nstrackingmousemoved"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", and "
        },
        {
          "type": "reference",
          "isActive": true,
          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstrackingareaoptions/nstrackingcursorupdate"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ") and one of the active constants (that is, "
        },
        {
          "type": "reference",
          "isActive": true,
          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstrackingareaoptions/nstrackingactivewhenfirstresponder"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", "
        },
        {
          "type": "reference",
          "isActive": true,
          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstrackingareaoptions/nstrackingactiveinkeywindow"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", "
        },
        {
          "type": "reference",
          "isActive": true,
          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstrackingareaoptions/nstrackingactiveinactiveapp"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", and "
        },
        {
          "type": "reference",
          "isActive": true,
          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstrackingareaoptions/nstrackingactivealways"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "). In addition, you may specify any of the behavior constants (that is, "
        },
        {
          "type": "reference",
          "isActive": true,
          "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstrackingareaoptions/nstrackingassumeinside"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ", "
