    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "When creating a tracking-area object, you specify a rectangle (in the view’s coordinate system), an owning object, and one or more options, along with (optionally) a dictionary of data. After it’s created, you add the tracking-area object to a view using the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483489-addtrackingarea"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method. Depending on the options specified, the owner of the tracking area receives "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsresponder/1529306-mouseentered"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsresponder/1527561-mouseexited"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsresponder/1525114-mousemoved"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsresponder/1525066-cursorupdate"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " messages when the mouse cursor enters, moves within, and leaves the tracking area. Currently the tracking area is restricted to rectangles. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "An "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstrackingarea"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " object belongs to its view rather than to its window. Consequently, you can add and remove tracking rectangles without needing to worry if the view has been added to a window. In addition, this design makes it possible for the AppKit to compute the geometry of tracking areas automatically when a view moves and, in some cases, when a view changes size."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Using "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstrackingarea"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", you can configure the scope of activity for mouse tracking. There are four options:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "unorderedList",
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "The tracking area is active only when the view is first responder."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "The tracking area is active when the view is in the key window."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "The tracking area is active when the application is active."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "The tracking area is active always (even when the application is inactive)."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Other options for "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstrackingarea"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " objects include specifying that the tracking area should be synchronized with the visible rectangle of the view ("
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483446-visiblerect"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ") and for generating "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "mouseEntered:"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "mouseExited"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ": events when the mouse is dragged."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Other "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " methods related to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstrackingarea"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " objects (in addition to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483489-addtrackingarea"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ") include "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483634-removetrackingarea"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " and "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsview/1483719-updatetrackingareas"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". Views can override the latter method to recompute and replace their "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nstrackingarea"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " objects in certain situations, such as a change in the size of the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "visibleRect"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
